<h2>3. What did not work</h2>
<ul>
<li>GLOMAP: I tried GLOMAP instead of COLMAP with the pre-clustering approa=
ch, but it didn't improve the score.</li>
<li>Coarse-to-Fine matching: Probably, there was a bug in my implementation=
.</li>
<li>Using monocular depth estimation: I tried to filter mismatched pairs us=
ing depth information.</li>
<li>VGGT: The tracking head of VGGT with pre-extracted keypoints worked wel=
l on local tests, but it resulted in a <code>TimeoutError</code> in submiss=
ion.</li>
</ul>
